name: Internal Dialogue
description:
I like this! It's finished! Look other people like it too. It's time to explore other ideas, learn new things, expand my horizons. Remember that list of potential concepts you keep adding to?

I just need to explore some different colours. Look at the piece that amazing artist just posted, your work isn't up to that standard, keep working on it. You'll never be that good.

An internal dialogue in Morse Code.
